## ⚙️ API Reference

| Method | Route | Access | Description |
|--------|-------|--------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/health` | Public | Health check |
| GET | `/api/projects` | Public | Get all projects |
| GET | `/api/projects/:id` | Public | Get single project |
| POST | `/api/contact` | Public | Submit contact form |
| GET | `/api/testimonials` | Public | Get approved testimonials |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Public | Admin login → JWT |
| POST | `/api/auth/setup` | Public* | Create first admin account |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | Protected | Get current admin |
| GET | `/api/admin/stats` | Protected | Dashboard stats |
| POST | `/api/admin/projects` | Protected | Add project |
| PUT | `/api/admin/projects/:id` | Protected | Edit project |
| DELETE | `/api/admin/projects/:id` | Protected | Delete project |
| GET | `/api/admin/contacts` | Protected | View messages |
| PATCH | `/api/admin/contacts/:id/status` | Protected | Update message status |
| POST | `/api/admin/testimonials` | Protected | Add testimonial |
| DELETE | `/api/admin/testimonials/:id` | Protected | Delete testimonial |

> ⚠️ `/api/auth/setup` creates the first admin. **Comment it out** after use!

