## 🔐 Creating Your First Admin Account

After deploying the backend, make a **one-time POST request**:

```bash
curl -X POST https://your-backend.render.com/api/auth/setup \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"username":"shivmani","password":"your_strong_password"}'
```

Then **comment out or delete** the `/setup` route in `routes/authRoutes.js`!

**Admin dashboard:** Visit `https://your-domain.com/admin.html`

