## 📊 MongoDB Schema Overview

**Project:** title, description, stack[], category, image, demo, github, featured, order  
**Contact:** name, email, subject, message, status, ip  
**Testimonial:** name, role, text, stars, company, approved, order  
**Admin:** username, password (hashed), lastLogin  

